- Now that is terrifying.

14:10.400 --> 14:13.567
The components of that triad
are important.

14:13.567 --> 14:15.900
It is unacceptable
not to be able to name

14:15.900 --> 14:16.934
every single one of them.

14:16.934 --> 14:19.834
They are nuclear weapons,
not your children.

14:19.834 --> 14:22.166
What is her name, Donald?

14:22.166 --> 14:23.633
What is her name?

14:23.633 --> 14:25.266
I'll give you a hint,

14:25.266 --> 14:27.367
it starts with T.

14:27.367 --> 14:29.867
And it's not "The Other One."

14:29.867 --> 14:32.200
And--and you would hope

14:32.200 --> 14:35.033
that as president,
he'd now be getting information

14:35.033 --> 14:36.600
from prime resources
and briefings.

14:36.600 --> 14:37.600
But Trump still watches

14:37.600 --> 14:39.667
a phenomenal amount
of cable news.

14:39.667 --> 14:41.867
His tweets frequently
echo things

14:41.867 --> 14:43.467
that just aired on TV.

14:43.467 --> 14:46.567
Just two weeks ago,
he tweeted "Ungrateful TRAITOR

14:46.567 --> 14:48.233
"Chelsea Manning, who should
never have been

14:48.233 --> 14:50.633
"released from prison, is now
calling President Obama

14:50.633 --> 14:52.233
a weak leader.
Terrible!"

14:52.233 --> 14:54.567
Which is interesting
because Chelsea Manning

14:54.567 --> 14:56.867
never used the words
"weak leader."

14:56.867 --> 15:00.066
But that phrase
was used on Fox News

15:00.066 --> 15:02.400
just 15 minutes
before he tweeted

15:02.400 --> 15:04.166
in a segment which also
called Manning

15:04.166 --> 15:05.967
an "ungrateful traitor."

15:05.967 --> 15:07.567
So the president seems to tweet

15:07.567 --> 15:11.233
about whatever information
he just saw on cable news.

15:11.233 --> 15:13.500
If someone changed the channel
to the Sprout network

15:13.500 --> 15:15.934
he'd tweet,
"Caillou's life is boring

15:15.934 --> 15:19.400
even for a cancer kid.
SAD!"

15:19.400 --> 15:21.400
Now, to give you a sense

15:21.400 --> 15:24.200
of just how much
he watches cable news,

15:24.200 --> 15:27.000
a few hours later
he was on "Air Force One,"

15:27.000 --> 15:30.233
